&gt; Frank, you&#39;ve been fair... more fair than I&#39;d be, in a similar situation.
&gt;
&gt; I&#39;m not hearing anything new or interesting from the complainers and
&gt; critics.
&gt;
&gt; I&#39;m here for conversations about... well, exactly what you said, &quot;what
&gt; these voices are, and how to hear it and interpret it better.&quot;
&gt;
&gt; Might some of this be pareidolia? Of course. We&#39;re not stupid... or at
&gt; least most of us aren&#39;t. Is ALL of it pareidolia? Not a chance.
&gt;
&gt; So let&#39;s get back to what&#39;s interesting: Searching for what the voices are,
&gt; how to hear and interpret what they&#39;re saying, and which ones to take
&gt; seriously. Let&#39;s find ways to hear them so even the most adamant skeptic
&gt; must concede that something interesting is going on here.
&gt;
&gt; (Of course, the very fact that they&#39;re still reading this list suggests
&gt; that, in their heart of hearts, they do find the voices interesting, and
&gt; deeply want to believe.)
&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Cheerfully,
&gt; Fiona
&gt;
&gt; --- In EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com &lt;EVP-ITC%40yahoogroups.com&gt;,
